{"tid":2373922,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一樣好中意玩「互動電影式」/「步行模擬器」類遊戲？","createTime":"2021-01-20T23:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T16:54:20.000Z","uid":235939,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"e80a3a572c5bb93db2b8cbc706813094aa2d34a4","tid":2373922,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:47:49.000Z","msg":"互動式電影：該類型遊戲特點是以類似電影的方式呈現，且著重編劇<br />\n<br />\n步行模擬器：遊戲嘅目的就只有不停咁「行走」，跟住作者嘅劇本一直推動前進<br />\n<br />\n利申呢排見到YouTube推介隻game叫「to the moon」就去down左黎試下，玩完之後感動到流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後發覺自己中意嘅game都係呢類(例如whats remain in Edith finch, 手機game：我在七年後等你)，唔知係咪人大左少左精力去玩d需要不停升Lv不斷失敗再調整嘅game，宜家嘅我反而更enjoy sit back and watch the show。<br />\n<br />\n互動式電影/walk simulator類遊戲雖然本質上同電影好似(都係重視劇情同演出手法)，但就係提供到一種遊戲先有嘅獨特浸沉感，令你可以更加投入角色/遊戲世界，容易得到體會/共鳴。有時玩呢d game真係玩到感動到喊(當然劇本都好大影響)，亦有種治愈心靈嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知遊戲台到有冇同好？有冇人可以推介呢類嘅game比我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e83849de4dd453652a60ac61f4afd4e0385536f","tid":2373922,"uid":78819,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:48:36.000Z","msg":"Tomb raider 2013計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩完好似睇左一套好長既戲"},{"pid":"bfb3cd5ed9b874be06aa406a80b030a432876cb3","tid":2373922,"uid":9633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"底特律"},{"pid":"fc05aab4fc67293bfc63d87d134d64fc6616c071","tid":2373922,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:55:50.000Z","msg":"超好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eaf944906f0bfe80890f46c1cf30c8fc4d927cb","tid":2373922,"uid":380859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-